"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-showbiz-tom-daley-dustin-lance-black-children-silver-olympic-medal-win-paris-b1173467.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Showbiz  Sign up to our free weekly newsletter for exclusive competitions, offers and theatre ticket deals    I would like to be emailed about offers, event and updates from Evening Standard.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 420, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourprivacy notice.\", \"from\": 421, \"to\": 444, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tom Daley's husband and two young children were among spectators cheering for the diving star and his teammate Noah Williams as the pair won silver medals at the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 446, \"to\": 623, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 446, \"end\": 455, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.7237946958700854e-52, \"text\": \"Tom Daley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\"}, {\"begin\": 557, \"end\": 570, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\", \"score\": 0.999998273608197, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Williams\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Daley and Williams came second behind China in the men's synchronised 10m dive on Monday but were all smiles after the event - with Williams pecking his teammate on the cheek as the pair held up their silver gongs.\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 839, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 663, \"end\": 668, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9920653030449155, \"rank\": 0.005924083691966627, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ahead of the games, Daley's husband, American screenwriterDustin Lance Black, shared on Instagram that their eldest son Robbie told his parents over a year ago that he wished he could watch his \\\"papa\\\" dive in the Olympics in person.\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 1073, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 878, \"end\": 886, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.6349974950251688, \"rank\": 0.5748090684171423, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 929, \"end\": 938, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2595614035276087e-32, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}, {\"begin\": 961, \"end\": 967, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Jackson\", \"score\": 0.9992598277959717, \"rank\": 0.0007407203967736604, \"text\": \"Robbie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Jackson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Jackson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The two young boys could be seen in the crowd at the Aquatics Centre on Monday, with Mr Black pumping his fist and cheering after one of Daley and Williams' dives.\", \"from\": 1075, \"to\": 1238, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1160, \"end\": 1168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mr._Black_(TV_series)\", \"score\": 0.9999999724368539, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mr Black\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mr._Black_(TV_series)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mr._Black_(TV_series)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The diving star's mother, Debbie Daley, was also cheering her son on from the stands.\", \"from\": 1240, \"to\": 1325, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1266, \"end\": 1272, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Debbie_Dingle\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.7873279928923648e-12, \"text\": \"Debbie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Debbie_Dingle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Debbie_Dingle\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Other spectators could be seen waving union flags and sporting \\\"Team Daley\\\" t-shirts as they watched the event.\", \"from\": 1327, \"to\": 1438, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking to theBBCafter competing, Daley said: \\\"This time last year deciding to come back, not knowing whether I would make the synchro team let alone qualify for a spot for the Olympics, and now to be here in Paris diving in front of my son, who's just right there, who actually asked me to come back, is just so special.\\\"\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1763, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1650, \"end\": 1655, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999677129, \"rank\": 3.2203618065276335e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He added: \\\"My husband has been there for me for this whole year and he has really taken the reins with the kids when I have had to travel and stuff and it's just so special that we get to enjoy this moment together.\\\"\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1981, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Williams grew emotional and asked Daley to speak for him when he was asked about what the silver medal means to him after his coach died following the Tokyo games.\", \"from\": 1983, \"to\": 2146, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2134, \"end\": 2139, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9925485950280215, \"rank\": 0.007506344179150198, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Daley told the broadcaster: \\\"I have never seen Noah cry in my whole life, and I know how much this has meant to him and to (his former coach) Dave.\", \"from\": 2148, \"to\": 2295, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2195, \"end\": 2199, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luke_Snyder_and_Noah_Mayer\", \"score\": 0.9987824477689373, \"rank\": 0.0009971820318238694, \"text\": \"Noah\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luke_Snyder_and_Noah_Mayer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luke_Snyder_and_Noah_Mayer\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Dave has been such a key part in Noah's diving success and career and it's very sad that he's not here to be able to see this, but I know both Dave and my dad would be very proud to see us going in and doing a really, really solid performance there for a silver medal.\\\"\", \"from\": 2297, \"to\": 2567, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2331, \"end\": 2335, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luke_Snyder_and_Noah_Mayer\", \"score\": 0.9987824477689373, \"rank\": 0.0009971820318238694, \"text\": \"Noah\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luke_Snyder_and_Noah_Mayer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luke_Snyder_and_Noah_Mayer\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Daley's father died in May 2011 after being diagnosed with a brain tumour five years earlier.\", \"from\": 2569, \"to\": 2662, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Last week, Mr Black posted on Instagram: \\\"It's been a little over 16 months since our eldest son, Robbie, shared with Tom that he wished he could watch his Papa dive in the Olympics in person.\", \"from\": 2664, \"to\": 2856, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2675, \"end\": 2683, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mr._Black_(TV_series)\", \"score\": 0.9999999724368539, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mr Black\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mr._Black_(TV_series)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mr._Black_(TV_series)\"}, {\"begin\": 2694, \"end\": 2703, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2595614035276087e-32, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}, {\"begin\": 2762, \"end\": 2768, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Jackson\", \"score\": 0.9992598277959717, \"rank\": 0.0007407203967736604, \"text\": \"Robbie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Jackson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Jackson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Apprentice makers urged to tighten vetting after candidate's social media storm  Traitors star reveals tragic family history leaving viewers devastated  Another contestant is unmasked on The Masked Singer  10 great gift ideas that earn you Avios  \\\"Yesterday Tom kissed our boys goodbye before entering the Paris 2024 Olympic Village.\", \"from\": 2858, \"to\": 3191, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3175, \"end\": 3190, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.294220662821405e-17, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Today I took our boys to see theEiffel Towerin this, one of my favourite cities in the world.\", \"from\": 3192, \"to\": 3285, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are so proud of Tom for all of the sacrifices and incredibly hard work he's put in to get to his 5th Olympics and to make Robbie's wish come true!\\\"\", \"from\": 3287, \"to\": 3438, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3413, \"end\": 3419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Jackson\", \"score\": 0.9992598277959717, \"rank\": 0.0007407203967736604, \"text\": \"Robbie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Jackson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Jackson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Daley and Williams smiled as they took to the podium after sharing a hug with one of their coaches following the final round of diving.\", \"from\": 3440, \"to\": 3575, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is the second diving medal of the Paris Games forTeam GBfollowing a bronze for Scarlett Mew Jensen and Yasmin Harper on Saturday.\", \"from\": 3577, \"to\": 3709, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3659, \"end\": 3678, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scarlett_Mew_Jensen\", \"score\": 0.9999999999977263, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Scarlett Mew Jensen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scarlett_Mew_Jensen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scarlett_Mew_Jensen\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Elsewhere in Paris, Team GB stars Tom Pidcock and Max Whitlock will be going for medals in their respective events on Monday, while the eventing team also competes for a place on the platform.\", \"from\": 3711, \"to\": 3903, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3724, \"end\": 3729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999677129, \"rank\": 3.2203618065276335e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3731, \"end\": 3738, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9994385726420569, \"rank\": 0.0005617416958769962, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 3745, \"end\": 3756, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Pidcock\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Pidcock\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Pidcock\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Pidcock\"}, {\"begin\": 3761, \"end\": 3773, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Max Whitlock\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT  1  Crime  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping  2  Football  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news  3  UK  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war  4  Lifestyle  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  5  Football  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed 